name: Aircraft Pack: Modern B737 Series (NG & MAX)
description: Brings the B737-700/700F/BBJ1/900/900ER/BBJ3 and MAX7/BBJ MAX7/MAX 8/ MAX 200/BBJ MAX 8/MAX 9/BBJ MAX9/MAX10 to ACEO. Not functional without ACEOTweaks-Core and ACEOTweaks-Aircraft. These B737s will only spawn from airline mods which include them.
